parameters: ...What's up? Little lady, you want to join the game?

Huh? Looks like you don't have enough for the bet. If you
want to play, bring at least 500 mon.
Heheh! I did it! Three wins in a row!

Hehe, what a good and honest kid. I'll gratefully take the
9000 mon. If you've learned your lesson, don't come back to
the gambling den. It's too early for someone as young as
you.

(Hmm... What a waste of money...)\c[2]--Karin lost 9000
mon...\c[0]\$
Ugh... I'm sorry. This is all I have on me...

Well, that's fine. I'll take all the money you have. Think
of it as a lesson and stay away from gambling dens.

(Ugh... It's frustrating, I was on a roll until halfway
through)
\c[2]...Karin Handed Over All Her Money And Left The Gambling Den...\c[0]

\c[27]Main event count +20, vaginal ejaculation +10, external
ejaculation +5, oral ejaculation +5, lewdness +10\c[0]

Somehow, it doesn't feel right... The opposite side of what
we bet always comes up--
...What's that? You're not suggesting I'm cheating, are you?

Hey now, don't glare at me like that. That's quite an
accusation. Do you have any proof, miss?

...I saw a thread inside the cup. You used a thread to
manipulate the outcome, didn't you?

What? Hahahaha! You're making me laugh! If you doubt it,
feel free to look inside.

...This. It's a thread, right? Even though it's dark in
here, I can't believe I didn't notice.

~~~~~~~~~~!!? (Unbelievable! This girl...! She snatched the
cup away in the blink of an eye!? )

Heh--Just because you have bad sleight of hand doesn't mean
it's your exclusive trademark, Mr. Cheating Cup Shaker.

Don't underestimate me, okay? Here's the proof. Are you
going to make excuses or not? Which will it be?
You bastard! Have you been cheating all this time--?

That's terrible! No wonder I kept losing until I had to pawn
my clothes! You swindler! Give back all the money you took!

You stripped me down to my loincloth with your cheating!
I'll never forgive you!

Eek?! Wait, wait! It's a misunderstanding--! I haven't done
anything shady!

Ah... this place is turning into a battlefield. Well then,
I've overstayed my welcome--
It seems the gambling den was closed down by Karin--

If you ever feel like playing again, just give me a call.
Heh heh heh.
(I don't have enough money. I should refrain this time.)

Heh heh heh. That's the smart thing to do. Gambling is a
man's world. I wouldn't recommend it for a young lady. You
should head on home now.

Phew... Looks like I broke even today. Just enough to win a
cup of sake. That's what being stylish is all about.

Dice-chan, Dice-chan... please give me the result I wish
for...

Hey hey, sis, do you have the money? If not, you'll have to
pay with your body.

Even-odd betting is simple, but everyone gets hooked on it.
You really love gambling, huh?

...What? What happened to the kimono? Oh, that thing's
already been pawned. Don't worry. I'll win today and get it
back.

Ugh... I've taken an advance on the money. I'm definitely
going to win today--! (shivering...)
